    "Through linear interpolation-based latency prediction for matrix multiplication, ReaLLM accelerates simulation while maintaining low error rates, enabling rapid evaluation of service-level objectives across diverse system configurations.",
    "DSD-Sim leverages the VIDUR framework as its foundation for modeling the performance of distributed SD, yet it maintains compatibility with all previously discussed LLM simulation frameworks.",
